OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780419953
OL,3,CTwo in court over death of mother who
OL,4,Cwas shot outside nightclub
OL,6,FTwo people are to face trial after
OL,7,Fappearing in court over the shooting
OL,8,Fof a woman in Sheffield.
OL,10,FShanice Brookes died after being
OL,11,Finjured outside the One Four Onr bar
OL,12,Fon West Street in the early hours of
OL,13,Fbank holiday Monday.
OL,15,FA 30-year-old man has since been
OL,16,Fcharged with her murder, while a
OL,17,Fsecond woman faces related charges,
OL,18,Fincluding assisting an offender.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
