PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780419953
OL,3,CTwo in court over death of mother who
OL,4,Cwas shot outside nightclub
OL,6,FJemele Rhone, of Outram Road,
OL,7,FSheffield, is charged with murder and
OL,8,Fappeared before Sheffield Crown Court
OL,9,Fon a video link from prison on Monday
OL,10,Fwearing a mask and sitting behind a
OL,11,Fdesk.
OL,13,FHis co-accused, Deiryen Dyce, of
OL,14,FEllesmere Road North, Sheffield,
OL,15,Fappeared in the dock flanked by a
OL,16,Fsecurity guard.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
