OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780419953
OL,3,CTwo in court over death of mother who
OL,4,Cwas shot outside nightclub
OL,6,FAlongside a charge of assisting an
OL,7,Foffender, Dyce, 32, is also accused of
OL,8,Fpossession of ammunition, possession
OL,9,Fof heroin, cocaine and cannabis with
OL,10,Fintent to supply, and possession of
OL,11,Fcriminal property, namely #2,000.
OL,13,FShe is further charged with possession
OL,14,Fof a handgun and criminal property,
OL,15,Fnamely #10,000.
OL,17,FA trial date for both defendants has
OL,18,Fbeen provisionally set for January 4
OL,19,Fnext year, with a furter hearing
OL,20,Fbefore then set for July 13.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
