FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780419953
OL,3,CTwo in court over death of mother who
OL,4,Cwas shot outside nightclub
OL,6,FRhone and Dyce were asked not to enter
OL,7,Fany pleas and remanded into custody.
OL,9,FBoth were charged on Thursday night,
OL,10,Fappearing before magistrates in
OL,11,FSheffield on Friday where prosecutors
OL,12,Fdescribed Ms Brookes as an "entirely
OL,13,Finnocent bystander"
OL,15,FShanice, 30, was a mother of one who
OL,16,Fvolunteered for Sheffield community
OL,17,Fcharity Zest and was on the cusp of
OL,18,Ffinishing a degree when she died.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
