PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1780419953
OL,3,CTwo in court over death of mother who
OL,4,Cwas shot outside nightclub
OL,6,FA statement issued by her family
OL,7,Fthrough South Yorkshire Police said:
OL,8,F"She could light up every room she
OL,9,Fwalked into with her infectious laugh,
OL,10,Fbeautiful soul and magical aura.
OL,12,F"Shanice made people feel loved, safe
OL,13,Fand valued simply by being herself.
OL,14,FShe was truly one of a kind and she
OL,15,Fwill be missed by all who were lucky
OL,16,Fenough to know and love her."
OL,18,FIn another statement, Zest said Ms
OL,19,FBrookes was "a truly beautiful soul
OL,20,Fwho touched so many lives within our
OL,21,FZest family and wider community".
